                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <!-- Defines an HTML form for user input -->
        </div>*@

    <!--BODY OF THE PAGE-->
    <div id="div1">
        <h2>At last, a solution to budgeting as smart and effortless as your phone</h2>
        <div id="div1txt">
            <p>Built for any smartphone, this is budgeting like never before. Simple to use, with instant updates to your fully customisable allowances, giving smart-reactive notifications as you spend your hard-earned funds.</p>
            <p>Budgie will always have your back, no matter where you are on the planet.</p>
            <img id="appstore" src="~/Content/appstore.svg" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="parallax1"></div>
    <div id="div3">
        <div id="div3txt">
            <h3 id="abouttitle"> Revolutionary smart budgeting at your fingertips, just for you, anywhere you go.</h3>
            <p class="myClass">Budgie monitors your budgets for you, allowing you to relax without having to think twice about your purchases. </p>
            <p class="myClass">If you are approaching towards your personalised budget limit, Budgie will notify you through your phone app, or via many different types of notifications (phone, email, text), fully customised by you.</p> <!-- paragraph -->
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="parallax11"></div>
    <div id="div3">
        <div id="div3txt">
            <h3 id="abouttitle">Budgie has taken flight because we all have smartphones in our palms today, but no smart budgeting to go with it</h3>
            <p class="myClass">We live in a world today thats expanding and innovating new tech faster than ever before and we need the right gear to stay in the race.</p>
            <p class="myClass">Our smartphones are with us all the time, when we are shopping, ordering food or even taking a taxi, but it still takes our banks days to update us on how we are spending.</p> <!-- paragraph -->
            <h3 id="abouttitle">We can change that. Budgie will always give you what you need, instantly.</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="parallax11"></div>

    <div id="div4">
        <div id="div4txt">
            <div class="offerSection">
                <h1 class="offerTitle">What does Budgie offer?</h1>
                <div class="offerGroups">
                    <div class="offerGroup offerGroupRightNow">
                        <div class="offerGroupTitle">READY TO GO</div>
                        <ul class="offerGroupList">
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">100% free! No hidden fees or service charges</li>
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">Contactless prepaid phone application</li>
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">Real-time budget notifications</li>
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">Usable anywhere in the world, with absolutely zero fees</li>
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">Instant transfers between Budgies</li>
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">Customisable, simple, smart budgeting</li>
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">24/7 first-class support</li>
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">Fully customisable UI to match your personal style!</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerGroup offerGroupUpNext">
                        <div class="offerGroupTitle">COMING SOON!</div>
                        <ul class="offerGroupList">
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">Supporting all banks, anywhere in the world</li>
                            <li><img src="~/Content/tick.png">1024-bit encryption protection</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="parallax2"></div>

    <div id="div4">
        <div id="div4txt">
            <p>Banks that are currently supported by Budgie:</p>
            <h3>HSBC, Lloyds, Barclays, RBS Group, Natwest, Tesco and many more!</h3>
            <img id="banklogos" src="~/Content/Hsbc-logo.svg.png" />
            <img id="banklogos" src="~/Content/LloydsBankLogo.svg.png" />
            <img id="banklogos" src="~/Content/Barclays_logo.svg.png" />
            <p> If you use a bank which isn't included, please let us know and we'll be support it.</p>
            <p>Budgie also supports other payment services such as:</p>
            <h3>Paypal, PayPoint, Stripe, Sage Group.</h3>
            <img id="banklogos" src="~/Content/PayPal.svg.png" />
            <img id="banklogos" src="~/Content/Sage.svg.png" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="myData"></div>
</body>
</html>

<script src="BudgieScript.js"></script>
